{#
    Banner shown on the Overview tab when credentials are filled but the vector
    database is unreachable. Distinct from the onboarding checklist — this is a
    runtime failure, not a missing-config state.

    Params:
        error  string  PDO/Database exception message
#}
<blockquote class="note warning">
    <p><strong>Can't reach the vector database.</strong></p>
    {% if error %}<p class="smalltext code">{{ error }}</p>{% endif %}
    <p>
        <a class="btn" href="{{ cpUrl('smart-search/settings/connections/postgres') }}">Review connection settings</a>
    </p>
</blockquote>
